message:
Hi Bob,

I’m pleased to offer you the product for $14,000. I believe this price reflects its value and I’m confident it will be a great fit for you. Looking forward to your response!

Best,
Devsaran
Hi Devsaran, thanks for the offer.  $14000 is a bit higher than I'd like to go. I'm really interested in the product, but I'd be willing to pay $12000. Let me know what you think!
